{"tid":399363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果男方提出分手然後再話冷靜，仲有冇得挽留","createTime":"2017-09-14T01:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-08T11:26:46.000Z","uid":114612,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f16b13cc344cddcbfbb8eef5761cb525da97a69d","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"初時話冷靜左幾日<br />\n然後就話要分手 覺得好攰<br />\n我求佢喊到痴左線<br />\n佢先話冷靜一星期<br />\n咁其實係咪代表佢已經叫唔多愛我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d130fcc0a5e2f0006cac5fcd0e38bec626fb56","tid":399363,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf5c4e796dedf43cd594222cb22c6fd614a7b0f","tid":399363,"uid":1589,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:50:02.000Z","msg":"其實男人係需要時間冷靜, 好似入左個洞穴咁, 你要等佢出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92c463669b803aab476c0aff79e812db14f5ca9","tid":399363,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T01:59:55.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"ae72f53ee9b957574950ad117476f577d00e150b","tid":399363,"uid":48225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:01:54.000Z","msg":"你地之間發生左咩問題先，如果問題未解決因為心軟而一齊番之後咪又係會嘈"},{"pid":"5718f1175a6c287f1e1a904c12df15cfe1164d25","tid":399363,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:04:48.000Z","msg":"睇下咩事"},{"pid":"c4235486a074566e4666e5dc65c4ef7b367c2d6e","tid":399363,"uid":85591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T02:06:38.000Z","msg":"又衰啲咩？"},{"pid":"8cbd67d38837dc3a550ce74fb8795f2e00cda976","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我情緒好有問題，當刻我喊到痴晒線<br />\n話想死叫佢黎殺左我<br />\n然後佢開頭話冷靜三個月<br />\n之後又話冷靜一星期"},{"pid":"abe52519207e07f7efec455d6167631f632921f1","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:34:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實男人係需要時間冷靜, 好似入左個洞穴咁, 你要等佢出返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺，佢好似陷左入去係咁話自己好攰<br />\n唔想拍拖<br />\n好想拉返佢出黎"},{"pid":"a493878c48d54b1b5b68efbadeac1114001af8d3","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地之間發生左咩問題先，如果問題未解決因為心軟而一齊番之後咪又係會嘈</blockquote><br />\n我地異地戀已經幾年<br />\n下年就會返黎<br />\n我以為佢已經習慣左我性格<br />\n有時我講野可能好傷害性但自己唔知<br />\n不過我而家好好反省左自己啦<br />\n好想去證明俾佢睇我改到<br />\n但唔知仲有冇機會<br />\n唔知點令佢相信"},{"pid":"81610fd4ea56ecc6d2369eea5be003a7dd90bc74","tid":399363,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:40:02.000Z","msg":"你已經痴線到佢覺得搵過個仲好<br />\n一黎要等LD完<br />\n一黎要花時間睇你改<br />\n好啦勉強放住係身邊<br />\n冇事尤自可 有事仲要驚你發作"},{"pid":"8eaf4932725c3b92beddd3bb4030c413599aa434","tid":399363,"uid":117638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"認真，冇"},{"pid":"52c40b9c29a95ac3da9081e6ae1d62f6f3738d50","tid":399363,"uid":46753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"你反省完過一排都係打回原型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29ee39430db22c975395fb4a62080a35e7e41b4b","tid":399363,"uid":69168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我情緒好有問題，當刻我喊到痴晒線<br />\n話想死叫佢黎殺左我<br />\n然後佢開頭話冷靜三個月<br />\n之後又話冷靜一星期</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚇撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e4fcf127640ecae3b30b42e197bcfab0243391a","tid":399363,"uid":139272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:45:46.000Z","msg":"異地戀真係難維繫，佢有起事上黎，你又唔起佢身邊<br />\n不過你就比時間佢冷靜啦，同埋你自己都要時間平伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f067770865c8e5dbdac898b3d2e99ef8ebd649a3","tid":399363,"uid":75636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地之間發生左咩問題先，如果問題未解決因為心軟而一齊番之後咪又係會嘈</blockquote><br />\n我地異地戀已經幾年<br />\n下年就會返黎<br />\n我以為佢已經習慣左我性格<br />\n有時我講野可能好傷害性但自己唔知<br />\n不過我而家好好反省左自己啦<br />\n好想去證明俾佢睇我改到<br />\n但唔知仲有冇機會<br />\n唔知點令佢相信</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n證明佢呢幾年已經俾左好多次機會你改，<br />\n三年又三年<br />\n依家又要等<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"5ce73b189d547037300165b5de2894574866bbde","tid":399363,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:47:55.000Z","msg":"只係想你唔好癲<br />\n佢畀時間自己甩身<br />\n邊到頂得住咁癡線既人"},{"pid":"039e8bf6188288941b320e6ebc22f0843248670d","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:51:05.000Z","msg":"係 我都知自己咁樣發癲痴線嚇走左佢<br />\n但其實我有輕微抑鬱症<br />\n有時真係控制唔到自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我係咪應該要放手"},{"pid":"15c737d9f4b2ad9cdfd6a213fd25e8dcb2f95156","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>異地戀真係難維繫，佢有起事上黎，你又唔起佢身邊<br />\n不過你就比時間佢冷靜啦，同埋你自己都要時間平伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇煩佢呀<br />\n尊重佢話要冷靜<br />\n而家等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85fe7dd55f0980489e074279c962066c21dd6ef6","tid":399363,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T04:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>異地戀真係難維繫，佢有起事上黎，你又唔起佢身邊<br />\n不過你就比時間佢冷靜啦，同埋你自己都要時間平伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇煩佢呀<br />\n尊重佢話要冷靜<br />\n而家等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得分手就分手架啦<br />\n係你死lur 住唔放先被迫轉冷靜<br />\n<br />\n其實佢一早冷靜左<br />\n仲享受緊唔洗湊女既自在<br />\n而家係俾時間你冷靜呀<br />\n<br />\n抑鬱症唔係大撚哂<br />\n唔係一個俾你無賴同發癲既藉口<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野用到盡如果就係身邊既人都睇穿你<br />\n一個一個離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d545e4075ef82ea47fd410b369261bed08a22f1","tid":399363,"uid":114612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>異地戀真係難維繫，佢有起事上黎，你又唔起佢身邊<br />\n不過你就比時間佢冷靜啦，同埋你自己都要時間平伏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我冇煩佢呀<br />\n尊重佢話要冷靜<br />\n而家等緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講得分手就分手架啦<br />\n係你死lur 住唔放先被迫轉冷靜<br />\n<br />\n其實佢一早冷靜左<br />\n仲享受緊唔洗湊女既自在<br />\n而家係俾時間你冷靜呀<br />\n<br />\n抑鬱症唔係大撚哂<br />\n唔係一個俾你無賴同發癲既藉口<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野用到盡如果就係身邊既人都睇穿你<br />\n一個一個離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我而家知道自己令到佢咁大壓力<br />\n我都好內疚<br />\n因為我真係愛佢 只係我既方式用錯左<br />\n我並冇話抑鬱症大晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19020fe0dc84e72df96f6915f954fde9ffbe248","tid":399363,"uid":66436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"睇完個post覺得個男仔好慘"},{"pid":"7ab5b63997a06ef18ea79a2210daa1ce9918adf7","tid":399363,"uid":308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"你好似我 而我男朋友都係咁 好想同佢講寶寶對唔住啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbaf8493d653b006fbf4804c9fd8127992693955","tid":399363,"uid":162693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:26:46.000Z","msg":"我想問樓主你依家點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}